thread.title: Emily

author: Emily
title: Emily
text:
We ordered a large amount (5,000) of custom designed calendars from printingcenterusa.com. The prints were very beautiful and the quality was wonderful! I was very pleased with the price for the quality that we got! This was my first time ordering with Printingcenterusa.com and I was very impressed with how the printed calendars turned out, the color compared to my digital file was very accurate! The templates they have available to download were very nice to start with! The customer representative, Mike, was great to work with and helped me with whatever I needed. I would definitely order from them again!
Emily
